  <p>
   The "right" sign for "ball" depends on what kind of 
			ball you are talking about.
   <br/>
   If you are talking about "a ball" as in "a dance" then you might 
			sign "DANCE" or just spell B-A-L-L.
   <br/>
   If you are talking about a large ball then you will need to do the 
			sign larger.
   <br/>
  </p>
  <p>
   The generic sign for BALL can (in context" be interpreted as meaning "
   <a href="../s/softball.htm">
    softball
   </a>
   ."
   <br/>
   <br/>
  </p>
